That's ¥12. Let's settle up first.

48
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,660
Good. Thanks!

49
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,960
 Crazy Good Bubble Tea! 

50
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,670
 Fall in love at first sip! 

51
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:45,590
- Thanks! 
 - Come back anytime!

52
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:48,090
Cutting in line is pretty rude.

53
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,460
Shu Lan!

54
00:02:57,990 --> 00:02:59,640
Lining up solo without us?

55
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,670
I was just passing by!

56
00:03:01,670 --> 00:03:03,920
This sugary stuff's not really my thing.

57
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,490
I'm just getting it for someone else.

58
00:03:05,490 --> 00:03:07,820
You heard the slogan, didn't you?

59
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:11,360
"Fall in love at first sip!"

60
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:15,920
Such an unscientific slogan.

61
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:20,460
Of course, our Ms. By-the-book Shu Lan had to come to conduct her own experiment!

62
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,620
Whatever you say.

63
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:27,660
Keep chatting about your lowbrow topics while you wait.

64
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:34,850
You know, with the current crowd and how slow they pour,

65
00:03:34,850 --> 00:03:37,600
it'll be gone by the time you get there.

66
00:03:38,365 --> 00:03:39,915
What?

67
00:03:41,146 --> 00:03:43,110
Was that really necessary?

68
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:47,680
But look at this line, it really is going to take forever.

69
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,420
Might as well bring a book.

70
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,460
We want five cups, please.

71
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:51,740
So, five cups total, right?

72
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:53,240
Okay, okay.

73
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:58,160
What, couldn't get enough yesterday, huh?

74
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,770
How many?

75
00:04:00,259 --> 00:04:01,923
Three. We'll take one for Si Qi.

76
00:04:01,923 --> 00:04:04,694
Wait, make it three per person for all four of us!

77
00:04:04,694 --> 00:04:08,984
Three per person... So that's one, two...

78
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,340
Hang on a second.

79
